# User Stories

## Reservations

As the reservation manager,
I want to search for a customer by name,
so I can quickly reserve seats without scrolling through the entire customer list.

---

As the reservation manager,
I want customers who have already purchased tickets to disappear from my contact list,
so I know who still needs to be contacted.

---

As the reservation manager,
I want to select multiple seats for one purchase,
so I don't have to enter the customer's information multiple times.

---

As the reservation manager,
I want the app to automatically calculate the total purchase price,
so I never have to use a calculator.
